video:video.video:title: Moscow gets ready for the new year with Christmas fairs, ice rinks and decorations
video:video.video:description: Moscow is preparing for the New Year celebrations. Streets and squares across the Russian capital have been decorated with festive lights and Christmas trees, while specially designated venues have opened to the public.

video:video.video:title: Macron says unity between US and Europe on Ukraine is 'essential'
video:video.video:description: On the last day of his visit to China, French President Emmanuel Macron said he discussed the need for a “strong and lasting peace” in Ukraine with Chinese President Xi Jinping and outlined Europe’s vision for ending the conflict.

video:video.video:title: New generation embraces steelpan almost a century after it was created in Trinidad and Tobago
video:video.video:description: The steelpan is making a comeback nearly a century after its creation as a new generation embraces its bright and melodious sound, both on stage and on the dance floor.

video:video.video:title: Brazilian Santa trades reindeer for jetski ride
video:video.video:description: Santa Claus arrived by jet ski at Rio de Janeiro's Copacabana beach on Thursday as part of a project to give children with a range of conditions a joyful day.

video:video.video:title: Superhero volunteers put a smile on faces of hospitalized children by climbing down clinic in Kosovo
video:video.video:description: Children at a paediatric clinic in Pristina enjoyed a special visit from some their favourite heroes on Friday.
